## 2. Feature Acceptance Criteria

<!--
  2–5 criteria per use case.
  Format: Given [precondition] / When [action] / Then [observable outcome].
  Test type label: Unit | Integration | E2E.
  Every Then clause must pass the testability test:
    1. Confirmable as true/false without human judgment
    2. Confirmable without reading source code
    3. Confirmable repeatably with fixed preconditions
-->

### UC-01: [Use case title]

**AC-01-01** `(Unit)`
- **Given:** [Precondition — specific system state, user state, data present]
- **When:** [Single triggering action]
- **Then:** [Specific, objective, observable outcome]

**AC-01-02** `(Integration)`
- **Given:** [Precondition]
- **When:** [Action]
- **Then:** [Outcome]

